# Use Angular MCP for Angular work

When modifying Angular code, generating components, or answering Angular questions:

- Prefer using **Angular MCP** (Angular CLI MCP) to look up current APIs, patterns, and recommendations before implementing.
- Use Angular MCP tools to validate or discover the recommended approach (e.g. signals, standalone, control flow) rather than relying only on general knowledge.
